  "texts": [
    "The main contribution and originality of this research can be summarized as follows:",
    "(1) Evaluating the CNN accuracy at different training-testing ratios to overcome overfitting problems.",
    "(2) Employing three CNNs of distinct topologies rather than using one CNN of unique structure.",
    "(3) Extracting deep features from the three CNNs and fusing these features.",
    "(4) Relying on spectral knowledge as well as spatial information to perform classification instead of using only spatial information which is not the case in previous studies."
  ],
